Bus Spider firmware
===================

Bus Spider â€” a better tool for DIY and hacking projects
that involve serial communications.

Bus Spider is inspired and heavely influenced by
Bus Pirate (http://dangerousprototypes.com/docs/Bus_Pirate).

Copyright (C) 2017, 2018 Antony Pavlov <antonynpavlov@gmail.com>

This firmware is free software: you can redistribute it and/or modify
it under the terms of the GNU General Public License version 2,
see the COPYING file for details.

Bus Spider firmware's source code is based on barebox bootloader sources.
See https://www.barebox.org/ for details.

Bus Spider firmware runs on Erizo SoC.
See https://github.com/open-design/riscv-soc-cores for details.
